<li>Your family is in our thoughts and prayers during this heartbreaking time.</li>
<li>We are saddened by the loss of your [Friend's Name] and offer our sincerest condolences.</li>
<li>May the love surrounding you help ease your pain during this difficult period.</li>
<li>We will always remember [Friend's Name]'s kindness and generosity.  Our hearts go out to you.</li>
<li>Sending love and strength to you all.  [Friend's Name] will be remembered fondly.</li>
